sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Browser as Browser / QA Runner
  participant Client as Client OTel SDK
  participant Server as Server OTel SDK
  participant Collector as Collector Boundary
  participant LGTM as Tempo / Loki / Mimir / Grafana

  Browser->>Client: Trigger action or QA playthrough step
  Client->>Collector: Emit client spans, metrics, and QA attributes
  Client->>Server: WS/HTTP message with trace context and telemetry envelope
  Note over Client,Server: ws.session_id, reconnect_attempt, qa.run_id,\noriginService, traceparent, tracestate, baggage
  alt degraded network / reconnect cycle
    Client->>Collector: Emit reconnect and heartbeat-timeout span events
    Client->>Server: rejoinMatch + replayed reliable msgIds
    Server->>Collector: Correlate reconnect path with same match.id and session metadata
  end
  Server->>Collector: Emit server spans, logs, and metrics
  Collector->>LGTM: Route normalized OTLP signals
  LGTM-->>Browser: Query by qa.run_id, match.id, ws.session_id, or game.match
